OL,7,FActor Gerard Depardieu has been handed
OL,8,Fan 18-month suspended sentence after
OL,9,Fbeing found guilty of sexually
OL,10,Fassaulting two women on a 2021 film
OL,11,Fset.
OL,13,FThe 76-year-old was convicted at a
OL,14,FParis court of having groped a 54-year-
OL,15,Fold set dresser and a 34-year-old
OL,16,Fassistant during the filming of "Les
OL,17,FVolets Verts" ("The Green Shutters").
OL,19,FDepardieu, who was not at Tuesday's
OL,20,Fhearing, had denied the accusations,
OL,21,Fsaying he's "not like that."
